x4freetext: MOST OF THE TARGETS WERE SELF-SUPPORTING,ISOTOPICALLY
ENRICHED FOILS WITH THICKNESSES RANGING FROM 3 TO
5 MG/CM**2.A SMALL STAINLESS STEEL CELL WITH
0.7 MG/CM**2 NICKEL ENTRANCE AND EXIT WINDOWS WAS
USED FOR ARGON TARGET.THE PHOSPHORUS AND RUTHENIUM
TARGETS WERE MADE FROM A COLLOIDAL SUSPENSION OF THE
MATERIAL WHICH WAS DEPOSITED ON A NICKEL BACKING WITH
.A PAIR OF 15 CM DIAMETER BY 2.54 CM THICK
.A DWBA ANALYSIS IN TERMS OF THE GENERALIZED
THE UNCERTAINTY IN THE ABSOLUTE CROSS SECTION IS
ESTIMATED TO BE 1. 11 PER CENT EXCEPT FOR P-31 AND
PB-208.2.FOR P-31 AND PB-208-25 PER CENT.3.RU-96 AND
RU-94 -50 PER CENT DUE TO UNCERTAINTIES IN TARGET
